{"tid":734900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【撼贏無綫黃金收視】ViuTV直播世盃八強賽事 138萬觀眾齊撐英格蘭","createTime":"2018-07-09T05:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:36:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"953804043073cb2a69e186182f4308c01fd5cfab","tid":734900,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:04:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180709/58419209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180709%2F58419209&d=EpBiDWHeHEVQSoaZVRr9hUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=cb7b46e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180709%2F58419209&h=2c96b357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180709/58419209</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018年07月09日 <br />\n<br />\n【撼贏無綫黃金收視】ViuTV直播世盃八強賽事 138萬觀眾齊撐英格蘭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0709 12:04<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180709/large/1531109020_fe3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180709%2Flarge%2F1531109020_fe3e.jpg&h=98c00035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭前晚喺俄羅斯世界盃半準決賽以2:0贏咗瑞典，成功躋身4強，今次亦係英格蘭28年來首次踢入世盃準決賽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭一向受港人熱捧，免費電視ViuTV前晚10點直播英格蘭對瑞典呢場重要賽事，當然受到全港球迷關心，據了解，呢場賽事平均收18點，有118萬人次，最高係21點，有138萬人次，比上次ViuTV直播英格蘭狂炒巴拿馬嗰場分組賽成績重好。<br />\n<br />\n至於無綫方面，據了解星期六晚9點半至10點半播《美女廚房》平均12點（79萬人次），跌咗5點、10點半至11點《3日2夜》平均6點（39萬人次），跌咗7點、11點至11點半《勁歌金曲》平均3點（20萬人次），跌咗4點，而11點半至11點45分播《晚間新間》平均只有2點（13萬人次），跌咗5點。<br />\n<br />\n至於法國以2:0淘汰烏拉圭嘅8強賽事，平均17點（111萬人次），最高19點（125萬人次），收視成績都好理想。<br />\n<br />\n之前ViuTV直播英格蘭狂炒巴拿馬6：1嗰場分組賽，已經創下ViuTV開台兩年以來最高20.5點收視，有134萬人次收睇，平均收視就有17.4點（114萬人次），仲令到ViuTV首次喺黃金時段撼贏無綫㖭。<br />\n<br />\n當晚《學是學非》平均只得12點(約79萬人次)，對比之前節目跌咗3點，而緊接《學是學非》嘅《冒險王衛斯理之藍血人》平均10點(約66萬人次)，比之前跌咗2點，而呢次亦係無綫自從2001年黃金時段輸過畀亞視嘅《名人慈善百萬Show》之後，17年來再次敗仗。當年《百萬Show》平均收視30點，而對撼嘅港姐決賽就只得平均21點，當年楊思琦攞冠軍，創下歷史新低港姐收視。<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊ViuTV會直播今個星期三凌晨2點法國對比利時，以及星期四凌晨2點英格蘭對克羅地亞呢兩場4強賽事，到今個月15日晚11點，更加會直播冠軍戰，相信到時收視一定再創高峰。<br />\n<br />\n一網睇盡 <br />\n足動世盃 直擊俄國最前線<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/worldcup2018/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fworldcup2018%2F&d=EpBiDWHeHEVQSoaZVRr9hUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f40c465a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fworldcup2018%2F&h=b5981c9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/worldcup2018/</a>"},{"pid":"a0d7b8dfcfc3b0d7e618feb1ee8b01420e382447","tid":734900,"uid":63450,"like":9,"dislike":18,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"可惜埸閪波仲悶過港超<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd9e511fbcea594f35e6f6fd7e91c134fdaf552","tid":734900,"uid":34685,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:06:22.000Z","msg":"cctvd仲話cut體育節目，執得"},{"pid":"d058fa08a2c88a175bed323593a757436e81714b","tid":734900,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"得幾點真係亞視收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02de785a56e8632f73a37554d3b8d8c2f7cee52","tid":734900,"uid":49588,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"支持祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/england.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c65317379b0086a9e1809ff7449d926e726f77","tid":734900,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"1.5億抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c9170d3e76152ab9616965cd8fd91d68219cd1","tid":734900,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05: